author: app.com
title: Football: Fisher's field goal lifts Ocean over Middletown North
text:
MORE MIDDLETOWN Ocean Township, a team typically led by star running back Tyler Thompson and talented quarterback Kenny Pickett, relied on a pair of unlikely heroes on Friday night against Middletown North.
The Spartans got a timely interception from senior Tyler Rossback and a game-winning 29-yard field goal from senior kicker Matt Fisher in the final minutes to pull out a 17-14 victory in a road showdown against the Lions.
